    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen searching for any string using `\\` or `?`, neovim searches every opened windows. It is both time consuming and inefficient as user might need results from only focused window. So an option to search only focused window will be very helpfull.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nOne possible way to address this issue is by adding a new value to option `hlsearch` which will only search focused window instead of all opened windows.",
    "closed_at": "2025-03-24T05:08:04Z",
    "closed_by": null,
